Class Segment

java.lang.Object
  com.vividsolutions.jcs.conflate.coverage.GeometryComponent
      com.vividsolutions.jcs.conflate.coverage.Segment

public class Segment
extends GeometryComponent

Represents a single line segment from the edge of a shell of a Polygon in a coverage. Maintains a list of Vertexes added during a conflation/cleaning process.
